<plot>A body-builder appears in a dark gym and starts working out. After some jump-rope, he starts concentrating on doing upper-body work, neglecting his legs in the workout. We then see that his muscles are growing significantly during each rep of the exercises, but since he's not doing leg exercises, his legs stay relatively small. Eventually, he's so top-heavy that he falls over, and is unable to get up again.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?180016</url></doc>
